N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 263.113 - Misconduct by any person

State Regulations

Misconduct by any person at any stage of a case before
the board, a hearing officer, or other person designated by the board to
conduct proceedings, may be grounds for summary exclusion by the board, hearing
officer, or other designee before whom misconduct occurred. Notes
